     <p class=\"name\">齋藤</p>\n                      </div>\n                      <figure class=\"p-card__profile__img new_delete\"><img src=\"https://g-jumps.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/営業部ルートセールス齋藤-scaled.jpeg\" width=\"100\" height=\"67\" alt=\"\" class=p-card__img></figure>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"p-card__interview\">\n                <a href=\"https://g-jumps.jp/interview/50819/\">\n                    <p class=\"p-card__title\">知識を広く学べ、現場に出てから役立っています　　　　　　　　(関綜エンジニアリング㈱)</p>\n                    <div class=\"p-card__profile\">\n                      <div class=\"p-card__profile__text\">\n                        <h3 class=\"company\"></h3>\n                        <p class=\"work-in\">工事本部　電気設備事業部</p>\n                        <p class=\"name\">大森　智史</p>\n                      </div>\n                      <figure class=\"p-card__profile__img new_delete\"><img src=\"https://g-jumps.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/先輩社員.jpeg\" width=\"100\" height=\"67\" alt=\"\" class=p-card__img></figure>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n\n        <div class=\"c-button-wrap\">\n          <p class=\"u-text -center\"><a href=\"https://g-jumps.jp/interview/\" class=\"c-button -main -right\">一覧を見る</a></p>\n        </div>\n\n    </section>\n    <!-- /.sec-interview -->\n  </div>\n\n\n\n\n  <div class=\"c-bg-deco\">\n    <section class=\"l-section sec-closeup\">\n      <div class=\"l-container -home\" data-sec-title=\"Close Up\">\n        <h2 class=\"c-heading -primary u-flex-align-center\">クローズアップ企業</h2>\n        <p class=\"p-lead\">群馬県の魅力的な企業を、働く先輩へのロングインタビューを通じて紹介しています。<br>企業紹介に加え、先輩方のリアルな声を通して働き方ややりがいなどが感じやすい記事となっています。</p>\n        <article class=\"p-contents-body\">\n            <div class=\"sec-closeup__wrap\">\n            \n            \n            <ul class=\"p-card__closeup__wrap\">\n              \n\n\n              <li class=\"p-card__closeup\">\n                <a href=\"https://g-jumps.jp/closeup/52337/\" class=\"u-flex-sp\">\n                  <figure class=\"p-card__img-wrap \"><img src=\"https://g-jumps.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/IP260617JOM000114000_00-1-scaled.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"67\" alt=\"\" class=p-card__img></figure>\n                  <div class=\"p-card__text-wrap\">\n                    <h3 class=\"p-card__company\">群馬ヤクルト販売（株）</h3>\n                    <p class=\"p-card__title\">群馬ヤクルト販売、熱中症予防に協力　高崎市等広域消防局が委嘱　訪問時にスタッフ啓発　高崎・上毛新聞（2026/6/18）より</p>\n                    <div class=\"p-card__arealist\"><span>中毛</span></div>\n                    <ul class=\"p-card__tags\"><li class=\"p-card__label\">環境問題に積極的に取り組んでいる</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">転勤なし</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">ISOを取得</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">日本一または世界一</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">地域の文化活動に力をいれている</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">資格制度、社員教育が充実</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">正社員採用</li></ul>                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"p-card__closeup\">\n                <a href=\"https://g-jumps.jp/closeup/52334/\" class=\"u-flex-sp\">\n                  <figure class=\"p-card__img-wrap \"><img src=\"https://g-jumps.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/IP260617JOM000092000_00-scaled.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"67\" alt=\"\" class=p-card__img></figure>\n                  <div class=\"p-card__text-wrap\">\n                    <h3 class=\"p-card__company\">ハルナプロデュース㈱</h3>\n                    <p class=\"p-card__title\">「潤う幸せ」を消費者の元へ　都内でハルナグループ30周年祝い感謝の集い・上毛新聞（2026/6/18）より</p>\n                    <div class=\"p-card__arealist\"></div>\n                                      </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"p-card__closeup\">\n                <a href=\"https://g-jumps.jp/closeup/52330/\" class=\"u-flex-sp\">\n                  <figure class=\"p-card__img-wrap \"><img src=\"https://g-jumps.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/IP260611JOM000191000_00-scaled.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"67\" alt=\"\" class=p-card__img></figure>\n                  <div class=\"p-card__text-wrap\">\n                    <h3 class=\"p-card__company\">株式会社両毛システムズ</h3>\n                    <p class=\"p-card__title\">助言受け技術活用　前橋高に両毛システムズ派遣・上毛新聞（2026/6/17）より</p>\n                    <div class=\"p-card__arealist\"><span>東毛</span><span>県外</span></div>\n                    <ul class=\"p-card__tags\"><li class=\"p-card__label\">株の公開（店頭・上場）をしている</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">資格制度、社員教育が充実</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">くるみんマーク</li><li class=\"p-card__label\">正社員採用</li></ul>                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n\n            </ul>\n\n            </div>\n\n        </article>\n        <div class=\"l-container\">\n          <div class=\"c-button-wrap\">\n            <p class=\"u-text -center\"><a href=\"https://g-jumps.jp/closeup/\" class=\"c-button -main -right\">一覧を見る</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- /.sec-closeup -->\n  </div>\n\n\n  </div>\n</main>\n\n\n<!-- footer -->\n<footer class=\"l-footer sec-footer\">\n  <div class=\"c-bg-sub\">\n\n    <div class=\"p-footer__container\">\n      <div class=\"l-container -wide\">\n\n        <div class=\"p-footer__flex\">\n          <div class=\"p-footer__form-wrap\">\n            <a href=\"https://g-jumps.jp/contact/\"><p class=\"p-footer__contact\"><img src=\"https://g-jumps.jp/cms/wp-content/themes/naganavi/assets/img/common/icon-mail.svg\" class=\"icon\">お問い合わせフォーム</p></a>\n          </div>\n\n          <p class=\"p-footer__logo\"><a href=\"/2028/\"><img src=\"https://g-jumps.jp/cms/wp-content/themes/naganavi/assets/img/common/header-logo-2028.png\" width=\"240\" height=\"80\" alt=\"ぐんま就活ナビ\"></a></p>\n          \n          <div class=\"p-footer__info-wrap\">\n            <div class=\"p-footer__info\">\n              <span class=\"text\">サイトに関するお問い合わせ</sp